# Stub response files read verbatim by VcrChatModelStubBuilder#respondingWithContentOf
# -- forced to LF on checkout regardless of platform (this repo has core.autocrlf=true
# locally), so the "read exactly as written, no trimming" guarantee tested in
# VcrChatModelStubBuilderTests holds identically whether checked out on Windows or
# Linux. Without this, a file committed with a literal trailing LF could silently
# become CRLF on a fresh Windows checkout, the same class of cross-platform fixture bug
# already fixed once in this project for structured-output schema hashing.
src/test/resources/stub-responses/* text eol=lf
